    "In the Metaverse, AI bots can be employed for a range of purposes, including sales, marketing, and customer support.",
    "It can assist users in the Metaverse by giving directions, offering details about goods and services, responding to inquiries from clients, taking orders, and even carrying out transactions on their behalf.",
